      "text": "אתם משה ואהרן דמומחי׳ נינהו:",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Nedarim 78b:2:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "ואין נדרים צריכי׳ מומחין. ולהכי"
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "סמך"
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "פ׳ נדר׳"
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "למועדי׳ לדרוש"
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "כן וע״כ תלתא הדיוטו׳"
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "בעי׳ כדפי׳ (ע״א ד״ה"
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "להכשיר)"
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "מדאצטרי׳ ראשי המטו׳ ליחיד"
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "מומחה: <big><b>הַשּׁוֹתֵק <span class=\"dh-divergent\">ע״מ</span> <span class=\"dh-divergent\">למקט</span></b>",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Nedarim 78b:4:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "שתצטער אשתו ובדעתו לבטל לה אחרי כן: <big><b>אֵימָתַי.</b></big>",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Nedarim 78b:4:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Nedarim 78b:4:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "<b>[אמרו] מת הבעל.</b>",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Nedarim 78b:4:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "<b>כו'.</b> היינו ברייתא דאייתינן ריש",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Nedarim 78b:4:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "פרקין (<a href=\"/nedarim/68a\">לעיל נדרים סח.</a>): <big><b>מַאי לָאו.</b> הא דתנן",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Nedarim 78b:5:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        4
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Nedarim 78b:5:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        4
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "שמע",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Nedarim 78b:5:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        4
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "ושתק ע׳׳מ למיקט וקתני",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Nedarim 78b:5:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        4
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "דהוי שתיקה מעליא ומהשתא",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Nedarim 78b:5:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        4
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "הוא לסמיך אדבסמוך דאי",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Nedarim 78b:5:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        4
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "בעי\"מ לקיים היינו שמע",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Nedarim 78b:5:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        4
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "וקיים: <big><b><span class=\"dh-divergent\">שותק</span> לְקַיֵּים.</b> כמו לקיים בהדיא",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Nedarim 78b:5:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        4
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "ואין יכול להפר:",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Nedarim 78b:5:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        4
      ]
    }
  ]
}